The Rt Rev.James Njegovan is the current Bishop of Brandon.[1] He was educated at St. John's College, University of Manitoba and ordained in 1979. He served parishes in Winnipeg before becoming Dean of Brandon Cathedral in 1992, a post he held until his elevation to the Episcopate.[2]
